  Connection&gt;scm:svn:https://somerepository.com/svn_repo/trunk&lt;/developerConnection&gt;     &lt;url&gt;http://somerepository.com/view.cgi&lt;/url&gt;   &lt;/scm&gt;   ... &lt;/project&gt; </code></pre> <p>Maven will use the information embedded in the SCM configuration to determine the used SCM provider (implementation) and the remote repository URL. The SCM configuration URL is composed of different information that define the mapping:</p>  <pre class="prettyprint linenums"><code class="language-unknown">   scm:svn:http://somerepository.com/svn_repo/trunk    &lt;service name&gt;:&lt;scm implementation&gt;:&lt;repository url&gt; </code></pre> <p>Check the <a href="http://maven.apache.org/scm/scms-overview.html" class="externalLink">Maven SCM list</a> for the list of supported SCMs.</p>
